  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Providing Safe Water for Poor Families</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will provide safe, pure water for poor farm families whose water sources have been found contaminated and needs rehabilitation. We will target 3000 families in this initiative. Aside from those lacking sanitary water sources, we will also provide drinking water to families affected by typhoons and other disaster. We ensure quality, safe water by the use of spring water sources and filtering them with commercial water filters. In this way we ensure the prevention of water-borne diseases.</narrative>
  </description>
